<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Home - CMS</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
</head>
<body>

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Complaint Management System</h1>
            <p>Fast • Transparent • Secure Complaint Handling Platform</p>

            <a href="/complaint" class="btn">Raise Complaint</a>
            <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline">Know More</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FEATURES SECTION -->
    <section class="features">

        <h2>Our Features</h2>

        <div class="feature-container">

            <!-- Feature 1 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3>⏱ 7-Day Resolution</h3>
                <p>
                    Every complaint must be resolved within 7 days. If not, it is 
                    automatically escalated to the Admin through a chain processing system.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 2 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3>👤 Assigned Responsibility</h3>
                <p>
                    Each complaint is assigned to a specific resolver (teacher, warden, 
                    mess incharge, or staff). Only the assigned person can resolve it.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 3 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🔄 Status Tracking</h3>
                <p>
                    Track complaint status in real-time: 
                    Created → Pending → In Progress → Resolved.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 4 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3>📧 Email Notifications</h3>
                <p>
                    Get email alerts on signup, complaint creation, status updates, 
                    and final resolution. Notifications are sent to both complainer 
                    and resolver for tracking.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 5 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🔐 OTP Verification</h3>
                <p>
                    After resolution, an OTP is sent to the complainant’s email. 
                    The complaint is marked approved only after OTP verification.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 6 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3>📊 Personal Dashboard</h3>
                <p>
                    Each user has a personal dashboard to view and manage only 
                    their own complaints securely.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 7 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3>📂 Smart Filters</h3>
                <p>
                    Filter complaints easily by All, Solved, Unsolved, and Delay 
                    categories. Available for Admin, Employee, and Student.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 8 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🛠 Admin Control</h3>
                <p>
                    Admin has full control: can resolve, delete, and reassign complaints. 
                    Manages the entire system efficiently.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 9 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3>📈 Complaint History</h3>
                <p>
                    View complete history of complaints including status updates, 
                    actions taken, and final resolution details.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

</body>
</html>